    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Effective date:</strong> July 28, 2025</p>

    <p>This privacy policy applies to the mobile game <strong>“Spy: Party Game”</strong>, developed by <strong>Yuliya Leshchanka</strong>.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We do <strong>not</strong> collect personally identifiable information (PII). However, we may collect limited anonymous data to enhance your experience:</p>
